        <h1>Shipping Information</h1>
        <p>At blcnwht, we understand that receiving your purchase in a timely and secure manner is critical. That’s why we offer various shipping options designed to meet your needs, wherever you are.</p>
        
        <h2>Domestic Shipping</h2>
        <p>All orders within the country are processed within 1-2 business days. We offer standard, expedited, and overnight shipping. Standard shipping is free on orders over $75 and typically takes 3-5 business days. Expedited shipping reduces delivery time to 1-3 business days.</p>
        
        <h2>International Shipping</h2>
        <p>We proudly ship to over 100 countries worldwide. International shipping costs vary by destination and order size, and delivery times typically range from 7-14 business days. Customs duties and taxes may apply based on the destination country’s regulations.</p>
        
        <h2>Order Tracking</h2>
        <p>Once your order has been shipped, you’ll receive a confirmation email with a tracking number. Use this number to monitor your order’s progress until it arrives at your doorstep.</p>
        
        <h2>Shipping Delays</h2>
        <p>While we strive to ensure timely deliveries, unforeseen circumstances such as weather disruptions or customs delays may impact your delivery. We appreciate your understanding and are committed to keeping you informed throughout the process.</p>
        
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding your order or our shipping policies, feel free to reach out to our customer service team at <a href="mailto:support@blcnwht.com">support@blcnwht.com</a>.</p>
